Below is a complete, production-ready static website scaffold using HTML, CSS (Tailwind via CDN), JavaScript, jQuery, and a modular structure. It includes dark/light mode, sticky navigation, scroll reveals, a modal, a contact form with AJAX submission, and well-commented code. A minimal ‚ÄúHello World‚Äù is shown in the index hero as requested.

Deliverables
- index.html
- about.html
- contact.html
- css/styles.css
- js/main.js
- js/utils.js
- js/components/navbar.js
- js/components/modal.js
- README.md

Note: All HTML pages include Tailwind CDN and jQuery CDN. The Tailwind CDN is configured to support dark mode via a class on the root element.

---

index.html
```html
